Class SignatureRecord

java.lang.Object

      org.ndeftools.wellknown.SignatureRecord

public class SignatureRecord
extends Record

Signature record.

Digital signing of NDEF data is a trustworthy method for providing information about the origin of NDEF data. It provides users with the possibility of verifying the authenticity and integrity of data within the NDEF message.

thomas
